# GitHub Personal Access Token for updating the Homebrew tap formula.
# The release workflow pushes to lancekrogers/homebrew-tap after each release.
#
# To create one:
#   1. Go to https://github.com/settings/tokens?type=beta (Fine-grained) or
#      https://github.com/settings/tokens/new (Classic)
#   2. Classic: select the "repo" scope
#      Fine-grained: grant "Contents: Read and write" on lancekrogers/homebrew-tap
#   3. Paste the token below
#   4. Run: just setup-secrets
#
HOMEBREW_TAP_TOKEN=<personal-access-token-here>
